CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780661501
OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,FJohn Cotton, former leader of
OL,8,FBirmingham City Council, said: "It is
OL,9,Fwholly wrong for anonymous sources
OL,10,Fwithin Birmingham City Council to
OL,11,Fclaim that no deal exists.
OL,13,F"Senior officers and commissioners
OL,14,Fwere not only fully aware of the talks
OL,15,Fbetween Sharon Graham, Lord Barber,
OL,16,FMayor Parker and myself - they had the
OL,17,Fdetails of the proposed deal and were
OL,18,Fengaged in discussions with Unite on
OL,19,Fthe terms of that deal."
OL,26,@pD@`OUuD@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
