CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780661501
OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,FHe said he had repeatedly resisted
OL,8,Fattempts to sack workers instead of
OL,9,Freaching an agreement.
OL,11,F"As leader, I consistently opposed
OL,12,Fthose forces who were pushing to
OL,13,Fdismiss our workforce, rather than
OL,14,Fnegotiate a solution.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
