OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council denies
OL,8,Fofficers were trying to get workers
OL,9,Fsacked.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "All lawful
OL,12,Foptions to end this dispute have been
OL,13,Fconsidered. Officers have never
OL,14,Frecommended dismissal.
OL,16,F"Extensive efforts continue to be made
OL,17,Fto try to find a financially
OL,18,Freasonable and lawful negotiated end
OL,19,Fto this dispute."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
