CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780661501
OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,FCotton also accused some within the
OL,8,Fcouncil of trying to "rewrite recent
OL,9,Fhistory".
OL,11,F"I regret that some are now trying to
OL,12,Frewrite recent history, misleading
OL,13,Fboth our citizens and the members of
OL,14,Fthe incoming council administration.
OL,16,F"Frankly, both deserve better.
OL,18,F"I urge the council to stop wasting
OL,19,Fvaluable time and negotiate a
OL,20,Fsettlement based upon this viable and
OL,21,Flegal deal.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@HO]sD@AOUxD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
