PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780661501
OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,F"I'm very happy to work with the fresh
OL,8,FLabour leadership team to support and
OL,9,Fadvise the new administration -
OL,10,Fputting politics to one side - on the
OL,11,Fdeal and my experiences, to ensure
OL,12,Fthis difficult chapter in Birmingham's
OL,13,Fhistory comes to a close."
OL,15,FBut Birmingham City Council insists no
OL,16,Fformal agreement was ever in place.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
