PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780661501
OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,FIn a statement, a council spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Birmingham City Council were
OL,9,Fnot party to discussions held between
OL,10,FUnite and Labour in the run-up to
OL,11,Flocal elections.
OL,13,F"Therefore, no 'deal' exists to 'hang
OL,14,Fin the balance' or 'pull the plug' on.
OL,16,F"The statement made in the run-up to
OL,17,Fthe elections by the then-leader of
OL,18,Fthe Labour group was made in a
OL,19,Fpolitical capacity and not as the
OL,20,Fleader of the council."
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOUxD@AOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
