CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780661501
OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,FThe council said it remained committed
OL,8,Fto finding a "lawful, reasonable and
OL,9,Findustrially acceptable settlement".
OL,11,F"Since the commencement of industrial
OL,12,Faction, the council has worked
OL,13,Fdiligently to find a route to a
OL,14,Flawful, reasonable and industrially
OL,15,Facceptable settlement of the waste
OL,16,Fdispute.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@cO]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
