PN,37110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780661501
OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,F"We will continue to do so with the
OL,8,Fnew leadership and administration of
OL,9,Fthe council, when it is formed, and
OL,10,Fwould urge Unite to engage with us
OL,11,Falso."
OL,13,FBefore last month's local elections,
OL,14,FCotton had said an end to the strike
OL,15,Fwas "within sight", claiming an
OL,16,Fagreement with Unite had been reached
OL,17,Fbut could not be formally approved
OL,18,Fduring the pre-election period.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@FO]wD@EOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
