PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780661501
OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,FLord Brenan Barbar, who helped mediate
OL,8,Fsome of the negotiations between
OL,9,Fstriking workers and the council, said
OL,10,Fthat "this dispute could have been
OL,11,Fresolved many months ago".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
