PN,37113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780661501
OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,FLord Barbar, the former head of ACAS
OL,8,Fand a Labour peer, said in a statement
OL,9,Ftoday that there was an agreement
OL,10,F"hammered out" in a meeting on the
OL,11,F23rd of March, and said, "instead of
OL,12,Ffollowing these instructions the
OL,13,FCouncil's officers, backed up by the
OL,14,FGovernment appointed commissioners,
OL,15,Fused a string of delaying tactics to
OL,16,Fimpede the instructions of the Council
OL,17,FLeader until it apparently became
OL,18,Fimpossible to conclude the agreement
OL,19,Fbefore the impending elections.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780661501
OL,3,CCouncil officers wanted to sack
OL,4,Cstriking bin workers, says ex-
OL,5,CBirmingham leader
OL,7,F"Both the Regional Mayor and I, having
OL,8,Fsought additional advice, were
OL,9,Fcompletely satisfied that the deal
OL,10,Fwould be fully lawful and deliver fair
OL,11,Fvalue for money in restoring a proper
OL,12,Fservice to the people of Birmingham
OL,13,Fand long-awaited fair treatment to the
OL,14,Fworkers in the dispute."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
